---
source: crates/runtime/tests/models/search.rs
description: "SELECT subject FROM vector_search(qs, 'second') order by score desc LIMIT 4"
---
+---------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                         |
+---------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Projection: vector_search(qs, Utf8("second")).subject                                                        |
|               |   Sort: vector_search(qs, Utf8("second")).score DESC NULLS FIRST, fetch=4                                    |
|               |     BytesProcessedNode                                                                                       |
|               |       TableScan: vector_search(qs, Utf8("second")) projection=[subject, score]                               |
| physical_plan | ProjectionExec: expr=[subject@0 as subject]                                                                  |
|               |   SortPreservingMergeExec: [score@1 DESC], fetch=4                                                           |
|               |     BytesProcessedExec                                                                                       |
|               |       SortExec: TopK(fetch=4), expr=[score@1 DESC], preserve_partitioning=[true]                             |
|               |         ProjectionExec: expr=[subject@1 as subject, score@0 as score]                                        |
|               |           HashJoinExec: mode=CollectLeft, join_type=Left, on=[(id@0, id@0)], projection=[score@1, subject@3] |
|               |             CoalescePartitionsExec                                                                           |
|               |               BytesProcessedExec                                                                             |
|               |                 ProjectionExec: expr=[CAST(key@0 AS Int64) as id, 1 - distance@1 as score]                   |
|               |                   RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(3), input_partitions=1                       |
|               |                     BytesProcessedExec                                                                       |
|               |                       S3VectorsQueryExec: limit=30                                                           |
|               |             RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(3), input_partitions=1                             |
|               |               BytesProcessedExec                                                                             |
|               |                 SchemaCastScanExec                                                                           |
